{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/TMDB\/documentation\/TMDB\/AccountAndLists"},"sections":[],"metadata":{"title":"Account and Lists","role":"article","modules":[{"name":"TMDB"}],"roleHeading":"Article"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/tmdb\/accountandlists"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/TMDB\/documentation\/TMDB"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Manage favorites, watchlists, ratings, and custom lists for authenticated users."}],"kind":"article","seeAlsoSections":[{"anchor":"Getting-Started","title":"Getting Started","identifiers":["doc:\/\/TMDB\/documentation\/TMDB\/Usage","doc:\/\/TMDB\/documentation\/TMDB\/AuthenticationGuide","doc:\/\/TMDB\/documentation\/TMDB\/ErrorHandling","doc:\/\/TMDB\/documentation\/TMDB\/TestingAndPreviews","doc:\/\/TMDB\/documentation\/TMDB\/DiscoverFilters","doc:\/\/TMDB\/documentation\/TMDB\/TMDB","doc:\/\/TMDB\/documentation\/TMDB\/TMDBConfiguration"],"generated":true}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Overview","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All operations in this article require authentication. See "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/TMDB\/documentation\/TMDB\/AuthenticationGuide"},{"type":"text","text":" to set up a user session first."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Favorites-and-Watchlist","text":"Favorites and Watchlist","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Add or remove movies and TV series from a user’s favorites or watchlist using ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/TMDB\/documentation\/TMDB\/TMDB\/Account\/MediaType","type":"reference"},{"text":" to specify the media kind.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ Add a movie to favorites","try await TMDB.setFavorite(mediaType: .movie, mediaID: 550, favorite: true)","","\/\/ Remove a TV series from favorites","try await TMDB.setFavorite(mediaType: .tv, mediaID: 1396, favorite: false)","","\/\/ Add to watchlist","try await TMDB.setWatchlist(mediaType: .movie, mediaID: 550, watchlist: true)"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Ratings","text":"Ratings","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Rate movies and TV on a scale of 0.5 to 10.0 (in 0.5 increments).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ Rate a movie","try await TMDB.rateMovie(id: 550, rating: 8.5)","","\/\/ Delete a rating","try await TMDB.deleteMovieRating(id: 550)","","\/\/ Rate a TV series","try await TMDB.rateTVSeries(id: 1396, rating: 9.0)","","\/\/ Rate a specific episode","try await TMDB.rateTVEpisode(","    seriesID: 1396,","    seasonNumber: 1,","    episodeNumber: 1,","    rating: 9.5",")"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Reading-Account-Data","text":"Reading Account Data","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Fetch paginated lists of a user’s favorites, ratings, watchlist, and recommendations."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["let favorites = try await TMDB.favoriteMovies()","let rated = try await TMDB.ratedMovies()","let watchlist = try await TMDB.watchlistMovies()","let recommendations = try await TMDB.accountMovieRecommendations()","","\/\/ With sorting and pagination","let sortedFavorites = try await TMDB.favoriteMovies(","    sortBy: .createdAtDescending,","    page: 2",")"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Lists","text":"Lists","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Create and manage custom lists using the v4 API."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Create a list","let result = try await TMDB.createList(","    name: \"My Favorites\",","    description: \"A collection of my all-time favorites\"",")","let listID = result.id","","\/\/ Add items (each item is a tuple of media type, ID, and optional comment)","try await TMDB.addItemsToList(listID: listID, items: [","    (mediaType: .movie, mediaID: 550, comment: \"Classic\"),","    (mediaType: .tv, mediaID: 1396, comment: nil),","])","","\/\/ View list details","let details = try await TMDB.listDetails(listID: listID)","","\/\/ Check if an item is in the list","let status = try await TMDB.listItemStatus(","    listID: listID,","    mediaType: .movie,","    mediaID: 550",")","","\/\/ Remove items","try await TMDB.removeItemsFromList(listID: listID, items: [","    (mediaType: .movie, mediaID: 550),","])","","\/\/ Clear all items","try await TMDB.clearList(listID: listID)","","\/\/ Delete the list","try await TMDB.deleteList(listID: listID)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Guest-Sessions","text":"Guest Sessions","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Guest sessions allow unauthenticated users to rate content. Ratings are stored temporarily on TMDB’s servers.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ Create a guest session","let guestSession = try await TMDB.createGuestSession()","let sessionID = guestSession.guestSessionID","","\/\/ Rate a movie as a guest","try await TMDB.guestRateMovie(","    id: 550,","    rating: 7.5,","    guestSessionID: sessionID",")","","\/\/ Retrieve guest-rated movies","let rated = try await TMDB.guestRatedMovies(sessionID: sessionID)","","\/\/ Delete a guest rating","try await TMDB.guestDeleteMovieRating(id: 550, guestSessionID: sessionID)"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://TMDB/documentation/TMDB/TestingAndPreviews":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/TMDB\/documentation\/TMDB\/TestingAndPreviews","role":"article","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/tmdb\/testingandpreviews","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Use automatic mock data in unit tests and SwiftUI previews with zero configuration."}],"kind":"article","title":"Testing and Previews"},"doc://TMDB/documentation/TMDB/Usage":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Instructions on initialization and usage of the 